query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.categoryId, p.regularPrice, p.salePrice, p.stock, p.status, pi.url 
FROM products p 
LEFT JOIN product_images pi ON p.id = pi.productId 
WHERE p.id BETWEEN 510025 AND 510036 
ORDER BY p.id;
